          <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1</NUMEX>, <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">20</NUMEX> mM denatonium and <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">10</NUMEX> mM PROP elicited a small
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">phasic</ENAMEX> response in the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">CT</ENAMEX> in the mouse <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">MO01F22</ENAMEX>.
          The <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">second</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT_DESC">group</ENAMEX>: amiloride, atropine and <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">TEA</ENAMEX>
